{
  "name": "@kernel.chat/kbot",
  "version": "3.55.0",
  "description": "The only AI agent that builds its own tools \u2014 and defends itself. NEW: AI Producer Engine for Ableton Live \u2014 genre-aware beat generation, mix analysis, arrangement templates, 200+ plugin catalog. Max for Live bridge (5 devices). 690 tests passing. Security: sandboxed forge (vm.runInNewContext), HMAC memory integrity, prompt injection detection, autonomous security_hunt. 567+ tools, 35 agents, 20 providers. Science laboratory: 114 tools across physics, chemistry, biology, neuroscience, social science, humanities. Finance: 31 tools for market data, wallet, DeFi, stocks. Machine-aware situated intelligence, cost-aware model routing, Bayesian skill routing. 11 local models (Llama 3.3, Qwen 3, DeepSeek R1, Codestral 22B). Runtime tool forging, MCP server, SDK. MIT.",
